{"tid":2068861,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民打扮成米奇米妮 慶祝迪士尼樂園重開","createTime":"2020-06-18T03:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T06:58:22.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"86b9fd95ea683aeda2dca2749b6a6d244aa89e73","tid":2068861,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:51:20.000Z","msg":"市民打扮成米奇米妮 慶祝迪士尼樂園重開<br />\n2020-06-18 HKT 11:03<br />\n<br />\n關閉多月的香港迪士尼樂園今早10時重開，有大批已預約的遊客到樂園遊玩。<br />\n<br />\n有身穿米奇和米妮老鼠服飾的市民說，對於事隔多月再到樂園感到激動，希望看到不同樂園的角色，又認為雖然不能近距離接觸他們，但可以看到他們已很滿足。他們表示，打扮成米奇米妮是因為迪士尼創辦人華特迪士尼曾說，「一切由米奇老鼠開始」，因此藉此慶祝迪士尼重開。<br />\n<br />\n另外，樂園邀請超過100個居於離島區家庭到訪，其中葉小姐與兩名子女同來，表示小朋友因疫情已留在家中很長時間，因此樂園一重開便帶子女來遊玩。有小朋友說，很期待與喜歡的公主會面。<br />\n<br />\n香港迪士尼行政總裁楊善妮出席儀式，歡迎遊客重臨，又感謝香港社會、醫護人員及迪士尼員工的努力。她透露，修城堡擴建工程已進入最後階段，將在本年稍後重開。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532742-20200618.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532742-20200618.htm&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=083871df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532742-20200618.htm&h=f137e1e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532742-20200618.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dd850605cd8313f11fe1678c736cd0d8b2ffbdf9","tid":2068861,"uid":11960,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyvUVy0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyvUVy0.jpg&h=d52bbfc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db21944b792e8e576b28b94b585d86b5d204eca5","tid":2068861,"uid":360159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd850605cd8313f11fe1678c736cd0d8b2ffbdf9","tid":2068861,"uid":11960,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyvUVy0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyvUVy0.jpg&h=d52bbfc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:55:42.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd3ad8f23de5bb2a4afbfb1f338d2d6ffdbed57","tid":2068861,"uid":307619,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:02:39.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"9edcf434c6ceba24e2df9973ba75d76a07ada232","tid":2068861,"uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:24:38.000Z","msg":"話時話，香港的迪士尼樂園我一次都未去過"},{"pid":"b9be93e5f394af1ae9a180b14497b06844aec6b3","tid":2068861,"uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:58:47.000Z","msg":"迪士尼重開實施防疫措施 遊客須遵循職員指示保持距離<br />\n2020-06-18 HKT 13:32<br />\n<br />\n因疫情而關閉近5個月的香港迪士尼樂園今早重開，因應當局衛生指引，樂園實施一系列防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n遊客排隊等候遊樂設施時，須站在白線以保持一定距離，職員在遊樂設施上分配座位時，亦不會安排陌生人坐在一起。現場所見，遊行都有遵循樂園職員指示保持距離，大部分遊樂設施都沒有坐滿。<br />\n<br />\n另外，遊客購買毛公仔等紀念品時，可以向職員拿取全新商品。有市民說，新型肺炎傳播力強，因此會向職員拿全新的商品。亦有市民不擔心多人觸摸過毛公仔會不衛生，因為回家後亦會清洗。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532781-20200618.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532781-20200618.htm&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=78d1a61c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532781-20200618.htm&h=be54c36b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532781-20200618.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8c8fd9f38dd34d77e56b194b8044068ee635f327","tid":2068861,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd850605cd8313f11fe1678c736cd0d8b2ffbdf9","tid":2068861,"uid":11960,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyvUVy0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyvUVy0.jpg&h=d52bbfc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:03:36.000Z","msg":"瘦20公斤做運動打扮一下會好睇好多"},{"pid":"eca301275b6189de3226830243285b7988233fa9","tid":2068861,"uid":107913,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個搞笑<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=198677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D198677&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=fc60727c\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.t